        "term": "Alcohol",
        "definition": "Organic compound where a hydroxyl group (-OH) is bonded to an aliphatic (non-aromatic) saturated carbon atom."
      },
      {
        "term": "Phenol",
        "definition": "Organic compound where a hydroxyl group (-OH) is directly attached to an aromatic benzene ring."
